  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "――っていう感じなんです、最近の琴乃ちゃん\nなんだかどんどん張り詰めていってる気がして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――That's how Kotono has been lately\nI feel like she's getting more and more tense…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 7.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "すっごく心配なんです\nでも……私の言葉も聞いてくれなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really worried\nBut… she won't listen to me either",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そうか……教えてくれてありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Thanks for telling me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 17.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "IMFのステージがうまくいった時は、このまま\n復活出来るんじゃないかって思ったんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When the IMF stage went well‚ I thought\nWe might be able to recover from here…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "うまくいきませんね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's not going well",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.6666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストは確実に実力を伸ばしてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest is definitely improving their skills",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "先日のライブは、評判こそ差がついたが……\nスリクスにだって負けてないと思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The recent live show had a difference in reputation‚ but…\nI think we're not losing to ⅢX either",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとうございます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Thank you",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにそう言ってもらえると\n安心しますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When you say that‚ {user}-san\nIt makes me feel reassured",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 41.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……だけど、世間の評価が変わるには\nどうしても時間が必要かもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…But for public opinion to change\nIt might inevitably take some time",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ネットやマスコミは「低迷するアイドル」という\nレッテルを貼りたがるだろうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The internet and mass media will want to label us\nAs \"idols in decline\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "そう、ですね……\n何か一つでも、きっかけがあればいいんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ that's true…\nIf only we had something‚ anything‚ as a turning point",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "きっかけ……か。そうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A turning point… yeah. You're right",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "……じゃ、私もそろそろレッスンに行きますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Well‚ I should go to my lesson now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、怪我には気を付けるんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ be careful not to get hurt",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.6666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3900.0000000000055,
          "startTime": 71.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 73.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（渚の言う通り……きっかけが必要だ。強くなった）\n（ちゃんと前に進んでいるんだ、と思えるきっかけが）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(As Nagisa said… we need a turning point. To show we've gotten stronger)\n(A turning point to make us feel we're really moving forward)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
