      "text": "お疲れ様。急な呼び出しですまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. Sorry for the sudden call",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、気にしないで下さい\n緊急のミーティングって……どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ don't worry about it\nAn emergency meeting… what's going on?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに伝えたいことが二つあるんだ。まず一つ目\nBIG4の一角『どりきゅん』が活動を再開するそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have two things to tell everyone. First\nDoriKyun‚ one of the BIG4‚ is going to resume activities",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "あのどりきゅんが……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That DoriKyun…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "どりきゅん……？　なんだか美味しそう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "DoriKyun…? Sounds tasty",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣ちゃん、可愛い名前に騙されちゃダメだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei‚ don't be fooled by the cute name",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_03_02_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "最近は活動休止して影をひそめていたので\n芽衣ちゃんが知らないのは無理はないですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They've been stopped working recently and keeping a low profile\nSo it's no wonder Mei doesn't know about them",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
