      "text": "BIG4でもナンバー3と呼ばれる超大物ですわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're super big stars‚ called Number 3 in the BIG4",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
